{"tid":1397004,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"迖哥：不想將直播商業化","createTime":"2019-08-02T09:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:35:48.000Z","uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99cfba905518bd23bc52387fa883e3723f1bc8cc","tid":1397004,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"牙jeff真係鬼馬啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做直播「堅」為興趣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不想將直播商業化<br />\n<br />\n筆者問達哥，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有這麼龐大的觀眾群，有沒有想過用來賺錢變做自己的事業？他坦言商業化後就會變質，所以沒有這個想法。</span></span>坊間有些公司聘「女生」假裝打機迷，穿著性感衣服「自拍」上 Youtube，滿以為性感美女「宅男」就會上釣，表面打機實際想背後在 Game 廠手中拿宣傳費。筆者問達哥會否參考這「手法」，請個「妹妹」一同上鏡打機，怎料達哥「霸氣」回答：「唔會！真「毒」係唔會有女，其實真係打機就專注打機，使乜攪咁多野，睇我都夠啦，所以唔洗女喇，行開啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2014/06/05/tak-gor/people-interview/ppl_interview/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2014%2F06%2F05%2Ftak-gor%2Fpeople-interview%2Fppl_interview%2Famp%2F&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=d9e4e2e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2014/06/05/tak-gor/people-interview/ppl_interview/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"92e5a84dbe057206fdf57ad8f1a40193683870ea","tid":1397004,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"岳不群<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cfd711f6b82d26075a644df41dea53b9bfe133","tid":1397004,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>2014</strong>"},{"pid":"feef26e6f0089433e95890298586661af1b7c0cd","tid":1397004,"uid":10210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"2014 年 同2019年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今天的我打倒昨天的我"},{"pid":"dc702e38561f5be04a1dd27f0